3.Non-blocking sockets
Make client/backend sockets non-blocking so one slow connection cannot freeze the whole load balancer.
4. Fix partial reads/writes
5. Right now you may assume recv()/send() transfers everything. Real TCP does not guarantee that. Add per-session buffers:
client_to_backend_buf
backend_to_client_buf 
8. Tests
- round-robin test
- unhealthy backend skipped
- backend recovery test
- multiple concurrent clients
- metrics endpoint returns expected values
Switch from poll to epoll

5. Performance tests
After poll() version works, build an epoll version.